org.springframework.web.reactive.result.view

接口 Rendering.RedirectBuilder

  • 所有超级接口:
    Rendering.Builder<Rendering.RedirectBuilder>
    封闭接口:
    Rendering

    public static interface Rendering.RedirectBuilder
extends Rendering.Builder<Rendering.RedirectBuilder>
    Extends Rendering.Builder with extra options for redirect scenarios.

    • 方法概要

      所有方法 实例方法 抽象方法 
      限定符和类型 方法和说明
      Rendering.RedirectBuilder contextRelative(boolean contextRelative)
      Whether to the provided redirect URL should be prepended with the application context path (if any).
      Rendering.RedirectBuilder propagateQuery(boolean propagate)
      Whether to append the query string of the current URL to the target redirect URL or not.

    • 方法详细资料

      • contextRelative

        Rendering.RedirectBuilder contextRelative(boolean contextRelative)
        Whether to the provided redirect URL should be prepended with the application context path (if any).

        By default this is set to true.

        另请参阅:
        RedirectView.setContextRelative(boolean)

      • propagateQuery

        Rendering.RedirectBuilder propagateQuery(boolean propagate)
        Whether to append the query string of the current URL to the target redirect URL or not.

        By default this is set to false.

        另请参阅:
        RedirectView.setPropagateQuery(boolean)
